G(2)=1 + G(2)/2 \implies G(2)=2
G(m) = \frac{1}{m}(G(m)+1) +  \frac{m-1}{m} G(m-1)
G(m)=G(m-1)+\frac{1}{m-1}
G(3)=2 + 1/2
